snippet.title: Froggy's Battle Trailer
snippet.description:
Froggy's Battle is coming to Steam in July 2023!

Master unique loop movement, build your dream frog with shiny upgrades, and you might be able to survive the ongoing waves of angry enemies and strong bosses!

Wishlist now on steam
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2424650/Froggys_Battle/
